    "Management": {
      "text": "Often self-limited mild disease not requiring treatment\nAzoles\nfirst line\nTreatment options\nItraconazole\n- 200mg 2-3 times/day orally\nFluconazole\n- 400-800mg/day orally or IV\nKetoconazole\n- 400mg/day orally\nAmphotericin B\ndeoxycholate - 0.5-1.5mg/kg/day IV\nLipid formulations of\namphotericin B\n- 2-5mg/kg/day IV",
